data.title: Final Fantasy
data.meta_description: NDS LIST - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides the titles of over 200 Nintendo DS game ROM files stored on a 32 GB microSD card. The ROMs cover a wide variety of genres, including action, adventure, role-playing, racing, fighting, puzzle and board games. Franchises include Mario, Zelda, Pokemon, Final Fantasy, Call of Duty, Ben 10 and many others.
